### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/health

### Register User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "Test123!",
    "name": "Test User",
    "phone": "+254712345678"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "Test123!"
}

### Get User Profile
GET http://localhost:5000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Create Booking
POST http://localhost:5000/api/bookings
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "booking_date": "2024-02-20",
    "booking_time": "14:00:00",
    "session_type": "peer-support",
    "notes": "Test booking"
}

### Get My Bookings
GET http://localhost:5000/api/bookings/my-bookings
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Create Story
POST http://localhost:5000/api/stories
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "My Recovery Journey",
    "content": "This is my story of recovery and hope...",
    "category": "recovery",
    "is_anonymous": false,
    "allow_comments": true
}

### Get Stories
GET http://localhost:5000/api/stories?category=recovery&page=1&limit=10

### Update Progress
POST http://localhost:5000/api/progress
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "date": "2024-02-19",
    "mood": "good",
    "recovery_day": true,
    "journal_entry": "Had a good day today",
    "self_care_score": 85
}